@startuml BobaLink_Single_Torrent_Send
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam participantPadding 20

title BobaLink — Sequence Diagram: Single Torrent Send

actor "User" as User #F3E5F5
participant "Popup UI\npopup.js" as Popup #E8F0FE
participant "Content Script\ncontent.js" as CS #E8F5E9
participant "Background SW\nbackground.js" as BG #E8F0FE
participant "BobaAPIClient\napi/client.js" as API #FFF8E1
participant "FastAPI\n:7187" as FastAPI #E3F2FD
participant "Go Service\n:7189" as GoSvc #E3F2FD
participant "qBitTorrent\nWebUI :8080" as qBit #E8EAF6

== Detection Phase ==
User -> CS: Browse torrent site
activate CS #C8E6C9
CS -> CS: MutationObserver detects\nmagnet: link in DOM
CS -> CS: parser.normalizeURL()
CS -> BG: sendMessage\nDISCOVERED_TORRENTS
deactivate CS
activate BG #BBDEFB
BG -> Popup: sendMessage\nUPDATE_POPUP
activate Popup #BBDEFB
Popup -> Popup: Render torrent list
Popup --> User: Show discovered torrents

== Send Phase ==
User -> Popup: Click "Send" button
Popup -> BG: sendMessage\nSEND_TORRENT
deactivate Popup
BG -> API: sendTorrent(torrent)
activate API #FFE0B2
API -> API: Build request + auth headers

alt FastAPI Path
    API -> FastAPI: POST /api/torrents/add
    activate FastAPI #BBDEFB
    FastAPI -> FastAPI: Validate torrent data
    FastAPI -> qBit: POST /api/v2/torrents/add
    activate qBit #C5CAE9
    qBit -> qBit: Add to BitTorrent engine
    qBit --> FastAPI: 200 OK + hash
    deactivate qBit
    FastAPI --> API: 200 OK + result
    deactivate FastAPI
else Go Service Path
    API -> GoSvc: POST /api/torrents/add
    activate GoSvc #BBDEFB
    GoSvc -> GoSvc: Validate + metadata
    GoSvc -> qBit: POST /api/v2/torrents/add
    activate qBit #C5CAE9
    qBit -> qBit: Add to BT engine
    qBit --> GoSvc: 200 OK + hash
    deactivate qBit
    GoSvc --> API: 200 OK + metadata
    deactivate GoSvc
end

API --> BG: Promise resolved

deactivate API
BG -> BG: Store in send_history
BG -> Popup: sendMessage\nSEND_COMPLETE
activate Popup #BBDEFB
Popup --> User: Notification: "Torrent added"
deactivate Popup
deactivate BG

@enduml